'''生物動力農法'''（{{lang-en|Biodynamic agriculture}}），又稱為'''自然動力農法'''或是'''生機互動農業'''，是一種另類的農業形式，非常近似於[[有機農業|有機農業]]，但包含多種來自[[人智學|人智學]]的概念<ref name=networks>{{cite book |title=Power of Narrative in Environmental Networks |chapter=Chapter 6: Narratives of Nature and Science in Alternative Farming Networks |vauthors=Lejano RP, Ingram M, Ingram HM |publisher=MIT Press |year=2013 |isbn=9780262519571 |page=155}}</ref><ref name=PaullJ>{{cite journal |last=Paull |first=John |title=Attending the First Organic Agriculture Course: Rudolf Steiner's Agriculture Course at Koberwitz, 1924 |journal=European Journal of Social Sciences' |year=2011 |volume=21 |issue=1 |pages=64–70 |url=http://ora.ox.ac.uk/objects/uuid:ad657ada-c977-4305-92a6-27439c4a7d5d |access-date=2017-03-07 |archive-date=2021-01-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210110150249/https://ora.ox.ac.uk/objects/uuid:ad657ada-c977-4305-92a6-27439c4a7d5d |dead-url=no }}</ref>，最先由[[魯道夫·斯坦納|魯道夫·斯坦納]]於1924年提出，是各種有機農業運動中最早提出的一個<ref name=vogt>{{cite book |work=Organic Farming: An International History |editor=Lockeretz W |publisher=CABI Publishing |year=2007 |pages=9–30 |isbn=9780851998336 |author=Vogt G |title=Chapter 1: The Origins of Organic Farming}}</ref>。

生物動力農法與其他有機方法有很多共同之處 - 它強調使用有機[[肥料|肥料]]。生物動力農法獨特的地方包括將動物，作物和土壤作為單一系統進行處理，從當地生產和分配系統的開始，其對傳統和新的當地品種和品種開發的使用的重點。<ref>[http://www.biodynamie-services.fr/_ressources/document/fichiers/26/agenda-2015-engl-2-.pdf 2015 Biodynamic Lunar and Planetary Calendar]{{dead link|date=November 2016 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}; Desmond Ansel Jolly, Isabella Kenfield, ''California's New Green Revolution: Pioneers in Sustainable Agriculture'', University of California Small Farm Program 2008, p. 114; Carl F. Jordan, ''An Ecosystem Approach to Sustainable Agriculture'', Springer 2013, p. 126; Arnaldo Walter and Pedro Gerber Machado, "Socio-Economic Impacts of Bioethanol from Sugarcane in Brazil", in ''Socio-Economic Impacts of Bioenergy Production '' Dominik Rutz, Rainer Janssen (eds.) , Springer 2014 ISBN 978-3-319-03828-5 pp. 193-215. p. 208; Board on Agriculture and Natural Resources, Committee on Twenty-First Century Systems Agriculture, Division on Earth and Life Studies, National Research Council, ''Toward Sustainable Agricultural Systems in the 21st Century'', National Academies Press 2010. ISBN 978-0-309-14896-2 p. 21</ref>生物動力農業使用各種草藥和礦物質添加劑用於堆肥添加劑和田間噴霧劑；有時候這些方法是有爭議的。<ref name=treue>{{cite web |url=http://www.nitrogen.de/bub/faz.htm#plan |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20030417075038/http://www.nitrogen.de/bub/faz.htm |date=13 March 2002 |last=Treue |first=Peter |title=Blut und Bohnen: Der Paradigmenwechsel im Künast-Ministerium ersetzt Wissenschaft durch Okkultismus |work=Die Gegenwart |publisher=Frankfurter Allgemeine Zeitung |archivedate=17 April 2003 |accessdate=15 November 2011 |language=de}} (Translation: "Blood and Beans: The paradigm shift in the Ministry of [[Renate_Künast|Renate Künast]] replaces science with occultism")</ref>

==科學性爭議==
生物動力農法的一部份主張現在被認為是[[偽科學|偽科學]]，缺少[[可否證性|可否證性]]，無法用科學檢驗。例如認為[[西洋占星術|西洋占星術]]中的星座運行會影響各類型作物的最適播種時間。生物動力農法也主張用[[民俗醫療|民俗醫療]]中的[[藥草|藥草]]製作有機肥，例如用[[蓍草|蓍草]]花塞進鹿的膀胱、[[洋甘菊|洋甘菊]]塞進牛腸、橡樹皮放在家畜的髗骨內再用[[泥炭|泥炭]]包裹埋入地底、或是把牛糞塞在牛角中來產生[[腐植質|腐植質]]。農學家認為用標準的有機農業手段就可以得到同樣的效果，而生物動力農法反倒更像是[[煉金術|煉金術]]或[[探地術|探地術]]，而這種教條式的法則反倒阻礙[[永續農業|永續農業]]的發展。<ref name="treue"/><ref>{{cite journal | doi = 10.1007/BF02349036 | last = Kirchmann | first = Holger | year = 1994| title = Biological dynamic farming – an occult form of alternative agriculture? | journal=Journal of Agricultural and Environmental Ethics | volume = 7 | issue = 2| pages = 173–87 | s2cid = 153540221 | ref = harv }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|first=Linda |last=Chalker-Scott |url=https://s3.wp.wsu.edu/uploads/sites/403/2015/03/biodynamic-agriculture.pdf |title=The Myth of Biodynamic Agriculture |journal=Master Gardener Magazine |year=2004 |ref=harv |url-status=live |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170829050320/https://s3.wp.wsu.edu/uploads/sites/403/2015/03/biodynamic-agriculture.pdf |archive-date=29 August 2017}}</ref>

